THE UMASS BOSTON TEAM ALSO WILL SUPPORT THE LPV THROUGH PARTICIPATION IN INTERNATIONAL LPV AND CAL VAL MEETINGS SUCH AS THE BSRN BIANNUAL MEETINGS, ESA LPV EVALUATION MEETINGS, AND SURFACE ALBEDO BRDF, BIOMASS, AND LPV SESSIONS AT AGU, EGU, FORESTSAT, AND SILVILASER. FURTHERMORE THE UMASS BOSTON TEAM WILL PARTICIPATE IN, PROVIDE SUPPORT FOR, AND UTILIZE DATA FROM FIELD CAMPAIGNS OF OPPORTUNITY TO ASSIST IN EVALUATION OF SATELLITE ALBEDO AND BIOMASS PRODUCTS.
